rce-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">高通承诺为印度的战略人工智能风险投资基金出资高达1.5亿美元</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">英伟达美股盘前涨超2%</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">美股高开高走</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">全球市场：美股三大指数小幅收涨 苹果涨超3%</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">谷歌母公司Alphabet：印度政府与谷歌DeepMind建立合作伙伴关系</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-eastmoney\">东方财富</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">美股反弹，苹果涨超3%，标普500始终难上7000点</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-18</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">印度首次举办超大规模AI峰会，25万人将涌入</h3>\n                <div class=\"news-meta\"><span class=\"source-tag source-yicai\">第一财经</span>2026-02-17</div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"news-item\">\n                <h3 class=\"news-title\">抖音集团李亮：炒作\"字节是恒科的最大空头\"很荒唐</h3>\n                <